commit.message: Added buttons for admin on course pages

On the course page, number of reviews is linked and jumps directly to the reviews

Added a ratings column to the courses table
Showing recommendations on each course page
Created a command to save the course recommendations into the database
Created a table to store course recommendations
Cleaned up sessions which have viewed more than 120 courses while generating the dump
Improved the messaging on "My Courses" notification to encourage user to review the course
Added a command to generate csvs for building recommendations
Fixed the styling of the popup signup form on the review page for the small screen.
Added a test for the new review signup controller flow
Reviews are created if you decide to login instead of signup in the review first signup later flow

Wrong default signup type
Added a scraper for iversity
Added a FutureLearn scraper
